    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >&quot;Re:|THM - Once upon a time&quot; is a rhythm game RPG that travels through reversed time. </h2>The rain rises from the bottom to the top, and defeated enemies come back to life. Meetings become separations, and the story heads towards the beginning. <br>Players will unravel the story of the separation of humans and monsters in reverse time. Experience the wonder of a world where time flows in reverse, something that cannot be experienced in reality.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2154940/extras/838042de6ea1375a6c391c922ce31aa9.poster.avif?t=1675976358\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2154940/extras/838042de6ea1375a6c391c922ce31aa9.webm?t=1675976358\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2154940/extras/838042de6ea1375a6c391c922ce31aa9.mp4?t=1675976358\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>The hero Astelro, who defeated the Monster King, kills the human king,<br> Ankh. Using the reverse device called &quot;Ex&quot; that only the king has, he reverses the flow of time. <br>What Astelro couldn't bear to lose even by going back in time...<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2154940/extras/0879d1e52482984230b9a4276aa6c7cf.avif?t=1675976358\" width=480 height=268 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Various wonders in reversed time</h2>The story progresses like a video being played in reverse. The story is unraveled by looking back on the hero Astelro's regrets.<br> Will he sometimes be tormented by his past actions?<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2154940/extras/9241d992fc2582334ec5d1766a26b364.poster.avif?t=1675976358\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2154940/extras/9241d992fc2582334ec5d1766a26b364.webm?t=1675976358\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2154940/extras/9241d992fc2582334ec5d1766a26b364.mp4?t=1675976358\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Real-time reverse rhythm game</h2>The biggest feature of this work is a rhythm game that can be reversed in real-time. Even if you make a mistake, you can immediately roll back and restart from that point.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2154940/extras/4e311e11d03c66b646273fdad3fd6a8c.poster.avif?t=1675976358\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2154940/extras/4e311e11d03c66b646273fdad3fd6a8c.webm?t=1675976358\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2154940/extras/4e311e11d03c66b646273fdad3fd6a8c.mp4?t=1675976358\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
